  "title": "Delicate Buttery Filipino Apricots Pancit Bihon",
  "description": "A lacto-vegetarian friendly Filipino dish featuring dried apricots and served in a scallop shell, this pancit bihon is a romantic and buttery treat. It is crumbly and delicate, perfect for a special occasion.",
