  "instructions": [
    "Rehydrate the dried apricots in water for at least 4 hours.",
    "Cook the pancit bihon noodles according to package instructions and set aside.",
    "In a large pan, heat the unsalted butter and vegetable oil over medium heat.",
    "Add the diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for an additional minute.",
    "Add the rehydrated apricots, cooked noodles, and soy sauce to the pan and stir to combine.",
    "Season with salt to taste.",
    "Serve the pancit bihon in scalloped shells.",
    "Garnish with additional dried apricots if desired."
